            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EMoses%20and%20Aaron%20stood%20with%20great%20confidence%20before%20Pharaoh%20and%20declared%20the%20Lordship%20of%20God.%20Then%2C%20with%20only%20a%20rod%2C%20Moses%20systematically%20dismantled%20Egypt.%20He%20took%20the%20offensive%2C%20not%20the%20defensive%2C%20and%20began%20demonstrating%20to%20Pharaoh%20who%20%22I%20am%20the%20Lord%22%20(Exodus%206%3A2)%20truly%20was.%20The%20rod%20and%20staff%20of%20God%20comforted%20Moses%20as%20he%20stood%20and%20watched%20God%20transform%20his%20staff%20into%20a%20snake%20and%20turn%20the%20Nile%20into%20blood.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWithout%20armies%20and%20guns%2C%20diplomacy%20and%20politics%2C%20or%20cleverness%20and%20reason%2C%20Moses%20prevailed%20by%20maintaining%20a%20relaxed%20anointing.%20As%20your%20enemies%20rant%20and%20rave%2C%20they%20do%20not%20understand%20how%20you%20can%20sit%20so%20relaxed%20at%20the%20table%20of%20the%20Lord.%20While%20they%20are%20delivering%20their%20tirade%20in%20the%20power%20of%20the%20flesh%2C%20you%20sit%20in%20the%20power%20of%20the%20anointing.%20You%20must%20learn%20that%20as%20you%20%22walk%20through%20the%20dark%20valley%20of%20death%22%20(Psalm%2023%3A4)%2C%20there%20is%20truly%20nothing%20to%20fear.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERelax%20and%20lie%20down%20in%20green%20pastures.%20God%20will%20fight%20%22Pharaoh%22%20while%20you%20feed%20at%20the%20table%20of%20the%20Lord.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Exodus.5:22-7:25",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EExodus%205%3A22-7%3A25%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_5_22%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Moses%20went%20back%20to%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20protested%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20have%20you%20brought%20all%20this%20trouble%20on%20your%20own%20people%2C%20Lord%3F%20Why%20did%20you%20send%20me%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_5_23%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%225%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EEver%20since%20I%20came%20to%20Pharaoh%20as%20your%20spokesman%2C%20he%20has%20been%20even%20more%20brutal%20to%20your%20people.%20And%20you%20have%20done%20nothing%20to%20rescue%20them!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_1%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EExodus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPromises%20of%20Deliverance%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20told%20Moses%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNow%20you%20will%20see%20what%20I%20will%20do%20to%20Pharaoh.%20When%20he%20feels%20the%20force%20of%20my%20strong%20hand%2C%20he%20will%20let%20the%20people%20go.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20will%20force%20them%20to%20leave%20his%20land!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_2%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20God%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20Yahweh%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x2018%3Bthe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EYahweh%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20transliteration%20of%20the%20proper%20name%20%3Cem%3EYHWH%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20is%20sometimes%20rendered%20%26%23x201C%3BJehovah%26%23x201D%3B%3B%20in%20this%20translation%20it%20is%20usually%20rendered%20%26%23x201C%3Bthe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%20(note%20the%20use%20of%20small%20capitals).%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_3%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20appeared%20to%20Abraham%2C%20to%20Isaac%2C%20and%20to%20Jacob%20as%20El-Shaddai%26%23x2014%3B%26%23x2018%3BGod%20Almighty%26%23x2019%3B%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A3%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EEl-Shaddai%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20means%20%26%23x201C%3BGod%20Almighty%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20is%20the%20name%20for%20God%20used%20in%20Gen%2017%3A1%3B%2028%3A3%3B%2035%3A11%3B%2043%3A14%3B%2048%3A3.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2014%3Bbut%20I%20did%20not%20reveal%20my%20name%2C%20Yahweh%2C%20to%20them.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_4%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20reaffirmed%20my%20covenant%20with%20them.%20Under%20its%20terms%2C%20I%20promised%20to%20give%20them%20the%20land%20of%20Canaan%2C%20where%20they%20were%20living%20as%20foreigners.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_5%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20can%20be%20sure%20that%20I%20have%20heard%20the%20groans%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%2C%20who%20are%20now%20slaves%20to%20the%20Egyptians.%20And%20I%20am%20well%20aware%20of%20my%20covenant%20with%20them.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_6%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20say%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%3A%20%26%23x2018%3BI%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20I%20will%20free%20you%20from%20your%20oppression%20and%20will%20rescue%20you%20from%20your%20slavery%20in%20Egypt.%20I%20will%20redeem%20you%20with%20a%20powerful%20arm%20and%20great%20acts%20of%20judgment.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_7%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20claim%20you%20as%20my%20own%20people%2C%20and%20I%20will%20be%20your%20God.%20Then%20you%20will%20know%20that%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20who%20has%20freed%20you%20from%20your%20oppression%20in%20Egypt.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_8%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20bring%20you%20into%20the%20land%20I%20swore%20to%20give%20to%20Abraham%2C%20Isaac%2C%20and%20Jacob.%20I%20will%20give%20it%20to%20you%20as%20your%20very%20own%20possession.%20I%20am%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_9%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Moses%20told%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20said%2C%20but%20they%20refused%20to%20listen%20anymore.%20They%20had%20become%20too%20discouraged%20by%20the%20brutality%20of%20their%20slavery.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_10%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_11%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20back%20to%20Pharaoh%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Egypt%2C%20and%20tell%20him%20to%20let%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20leave%20his%20country.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_12%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%26%23x201D%3B%20Moses%20objected.%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20own%20people%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20me%20anymore.%20How%20can%20I%20expect%20Pharaoh%20to%20listen%3F%20I%26%23x2019%3Bm%20such%20a%20clumsy%20speaker!%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E6%3A12%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EI%20have%20uncircumcised%20lips%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%206%3A30.%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_13%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20spoke%20to%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%20and%20gave%20them%20orders%20for%20the%20Israelites%20and%20for%20Pharaoh%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Egypt.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20commanded%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%20to%20lead%20the%20people%20of%20Israel%20out%20of%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_14%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20Ancestors%20of%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20ancestors%20of%20some%20of%20the%20clans%20of%20Israel%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging-sp%22%3EThe%20sons%20of%20Reuben%2C%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20oldest%20son%2C%20were%20Hanoch%2C%20Pallu%2C%20Hezron%2C%20and%20Carmi.%20Their%20descendants%20became%20the%20clans%20of%20Reuben.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_15%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20sons%20of%20Simeon%20were%20Jemuel%2C%20Jamin%2C%20Ohad%2C%20Jakin%2C%20Zohar%2C%20and%20Shaul.%20(Shaul%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mother%20was%20a%20Canaanite%20woman.)%20Their%20descendants%20became%20the%20clans%20of%20Simeon.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_16%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EThese%20are%20the%20descendants%20of%20Levi%2C%20as%20listed%20in%20their%20family%20records%3A%20The%20sons%20of%20Levi%20were%20Gershon%2C%20Kohath%2C%20and%20Merari.%20(Levi%20lived%20to%20be%20137%26%23xA0%3Byears%20old.)%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_17%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20descendants%20of%20Gershon%20included%20Libni%20and%20Shimei%2C%20each%20of%20whom%20became%20the%20ancestor%20of%20a%20clan.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_18%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20descendants%20of%20Kohath%20included%20Amram%2C%20Izhar%2C%20Hebron%2C%20and%20Uzziel.%20(Kohath%20lived%20to%20be%20133%26%23xA0%3Byears%20old.)%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_19%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20descendants%20of%20Merari%20included%20Mahli%20and%20Mushi.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3EThese%20are%20the%20clans%20of%20the%20Levites%2C%20as%20listed%20in%20their%20family%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_20%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EAmram%20married%20his%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20sister%20Jochebed%2C%20and%20she%20gave%20birth%20to%20his%20sons%2C%20Aaron%20and%20Moses.%20(Amram%20lived%20to%20be%20137%26%23xA0%3Byears%20old.)%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_21%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20sons%20of%20Izhar%20were%20Korah%2C%20Nepheg%2C%20and%20Zicri.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_22%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20sons%20of%20Uzziel%20were%20Mishael%2C%20Elzaphan%2C%20and%20Sithri.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_23%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EAaron%20married%20Elisheba%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Amminadab%20and%20sister%20of%20Nahshon%2C%20and%20she%20gave%20birth%20to%20his%20sons%2C%20Nadab%2C%20Abihu%2C%20Eleazar%2C%20and%20Ithamar.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22exod_6_24%22%20bk%3D%22exod%22%20ch%3D%226%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%2